passwordMustAtLeast12: Password length must be at least 12 characters
passwordMustAtLeast2Digits: Password must have at least 2 numeric cases (0-9)
passwordMustAtLeast3Upper: Password must have at least 3 uppercase characters (A-Z)
passwordMustAtLeast3Lower: Password must have at least 3 lowercase characters (a-z)
passwordMustAtLeastSpecial: Password must have at least a special character
passwordRules:
Node Password Complexity Rules:

  • Only A-Z a-z 0-9 !#$%&()*+,-.:<=>?@[]^_`{|}~ characters are allowed
  • minimum password length is 12
  • it must contain at least 2 numeric cases (0-9)
  • it must contain at least 3 uppercase characters (A-Z)
  • it must contain at least 3 lowercase characters (a-z)
  • it must contain a special character
  • it must not contain username
passkeyRules:
Passkey Complexity Rules:

  • Only A-Z a-z 0-9 !#$%&()*+,-.:<=>?@[]^_`{|}~ characters are allowed
  • minimum passkey length is 8
  • maximum passkey length is 32
passkeyMustAtLeast8: Passkey length must be at least 8 characters
